<<

DescUsage: <<
To run Java programs that use this library, you may need to set
java.library.path and DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH to %p/lib. For example:

  export DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=%p/lib
  java -Djava.library.path=%p/lib Demo
<<

 	  	 
